data.description: HIGHLY MOTIVATED SELLER!! Embark on a journey through this large, bright, & irresistibly cheerful 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home. The thoughtful design ensures a seamless flow throughout, perfect for daily living & grand entertaining alike. Upon entering, you will be greeted by a formal dining room setting the stage for memorable dinners. The expansive living room beckons you to relax and unwind, while the cozy den provides a more intimate space for gatherings. Three generously sized bedrooms on the main floor boast large walk-in closets, providing ample storage & organization. The secluded master suite resides on the upper floor, offering a tranquil retreat complete w/ a private balcony — the ideal spot for morning coffees & evening stargazing. Large upright freezer in the laundry room. Two gas fireplaces, 1 in the dining room & 1 in the living room, add a touch of warmth and ambiance to this already inviting atmosphere. The property also features a paved driveway leading to an oversized 2-car carport, safeguarding your vehicles and outdoor equipment. The large, gentle fenced yard invites endless outdoor activities and landscaping potential. Situated in a prime location, this home is less than 5 miles away from the heart of town, acclaimed schools, making it convenient for work, education, and recreation.
